<section class="info-block">
	<div class="text-box" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Organization">
		<div class="body"><div><h1>Welcome</h1></div><div><p>Established in 1973, the Ontario Jewish Archives, Blankenstein Family Heritage Centre acquires, preserves and makes available documentary sources related to Ontario's Jewish community.</p></div></div>
	</div>
	<div class="blocks"><div class="box"><div class="box donate">
	<div class="image-area">
