			</div>
	<div class="holder">
		<h3 class="title">Search the Archives</h3>
		<div class="description">
			<p><span>Access our extensive archival collections online</span></p>
		</div>
					<a href="http://www.ontariojewisharchives.org/Research" target="" title="Start your research now" rel="7" class="link more">Start your research now &raquo;</a>
